  Goa2 tng2-khi3 lu2-koan2, jip8-khi3 goa2 e5 pang5-keng, chiong mng5 so2 khi2--lai5, goa2 chiu7 kui7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 seng2-chhat goa2 sou2 choe3 e5. Hit si5 goa2 thau5 chit8-pai2 beng5-beng5 khoaN3 chhut Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7 peng3 m7-si7 Ki-tok e5 Kau3-hoe7. Goa2 beng5-pek8 chit8-hang7 thang kiaN-hiaN5 e5 chin-li2, peng3 m7-si7 tui3 Sin-kau3-tou5 a2-si7 i e5 tui3-tek8 e5 chhui3-tiong, si7 tui3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2-kau3 pun2 sin e5 chhui3 tiong tit-tioh8 e5. Goa2 i2-keng khoaN3-chhut tu5-liau2 goa2 ti7 chit-tiuN heng5-sek siong7 e5 khe3-iok-su, hong3-khi3 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 i2-goa7, goa2 boe7 thang koh tiam3 ti7 in tiong-kan. Hit-si5 goa2 chai goa2 tioh8 sui5-si5 hong3-khi3 Lo5-ma2 Thian-chu2 kau3-hoe7. Chong2-si7, oh! goa2 e5 peng5-iu2, u7 chit8-phiN3 ou-hun5 kham3-bat8 goa2! Ti7 chit-e5 ou-am3 tiong, goa2 au5-kio3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 e5 Siong7-te3, goa2 e5 Siong7-te3, goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 ui7 sim2-mih8 hou7 chiah-nih ou e5 hun5 pau-ui5 leh?¡¨ 
